{
  "stem": "7414.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I told them, we have to go, because somehow, I did not expect the German, but I, I was afraid of the Russian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told them, we have to go over the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they did not want, because my brother left a wife with a small child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My brother-in-law left my sister, who was pregnant then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they wanted to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then, we were told about those 500.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was in Przemysl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES] My father was in Przemysl, and that was a funny thing, because when they come to the house, they were looking for my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was going down to the janitor's to get the-- and the German met him on the stairs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES] You see, my father did not look very Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was tall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very handsome.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- and the German, if somebody did not point-- if he hasn't got a beard, and somebody did not point to [? that, ?] they did not recognize [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they passed my father and asked him where [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Babat ?] lives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my brother-in-law was not there at home, because he was with us over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then, of course, we saw the Russian cross the border, because we were on the border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were going back to our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- and I will tell you that we still-- we were going through the Ukrainian villages and the Polish villages, and nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were friendly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us eat-- to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us shelter, and we still felt safe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we come back--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, well, next day, when the Russian were coming, we started to go back, which did not take it.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
